Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:22:59.24,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\3c&HC7842C&}call me distortion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.24,0:23:01.97,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H6F&}请别记恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.97,0:23:10.91,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur5\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H6F&}这柄匕首本该是你美丽的未来
